    dc:creator "Dzik, Jerzy; Ivantsov, Andrey Yu.; Deulin, Yuriy V." ;
    dc:date "2004" ;
    dc:title "Oldest shrimp and associated phyllocarid from the Lower Devonian of northern Russia" ;
